{"type": "article", "id": 22879, "title": "天气魔方", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 187, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021441110VZWpfcbnoeSk8qa.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款可以显示温度和时间的 Weather Cube 天气魔方，更重要的是它通过超声波影响玻璃盒子里水的状况来显示天气。晴天时水面平静，起风时水面也有波浪，到了雨天则玻璃上挂满水滴，让天气和时间的信息都浓缩在一个小的盒子里，是一组可视化的设计。产品由两位设计师合作，设计师庄愉出身于浙江，目前在日本东京工作，<a href=\"http://www.designshoyu.com/404171/gallery\">这里是他的设计主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144108MkFiSb9XQLPv0oOC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021441094NlQsWB1xnZuXCgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144109ETrsgx9FCQ5Rpvn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144110aHONJXVxWh048qwl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021441101IipfNPkUt7uy0l8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}